    <section class="hero-section text-center text-white py-5" style="background-color: #004080; background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-4">Empower Your Business with E-Invoicing</h1>
            <p class="lead mt-3">Simplify invoicing, reduce errors, and stay compliant. Let us handle the details.</p>
            
            <img width="150" class="img-fluid mb-4" src="./images/e-invoice.png" alt="e-invoice" />
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <section class="header-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center">
                
                <h1>What is an E-Invoice?</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                    E-Invoicing is the electronic generation and exchange of invoices between buyers and sellers in a standardized digital format. It streamlines invoicing processes, reduces paperwork, and improves accuracy.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Description Section -->
    <section class="content-section py-5 bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-10">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Why E-Invoicing Matters</h2>
                    <p class="text-center">
                        E-Invoicing transforms the traditional invoicing process by replacing paper-based invoices with a digital alternative that can be processed faster, more accurately, and with greater transparency.
                        It enables organizations to automate their financial workflows, reducing errors, speeding up payments, and complying with tax regulations.
                        The adoption of e-invoicing is not only a step towards digital transformation but also a necessity in today’s business landscape.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Advantages Section -->
    <section class="content-section advantages-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Advantages of E-Invoicing</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Advantage 1 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="advantage-card p-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/icon-savings.png" alt="Cost Savings" width="50" class="mb-3">
                        <h5>Cost Savings</h5>
                        <p>Reduce printing, postage, and paper costs by transitioning to a digital invoicing system. E-invoicing also cuts down on manual handling and errors, leading to more efficient operations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Advantage 2 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="advantage-card p-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/icon-accuracy.png" alt="Improved Accuracy" width="50" class="mb-3">
                        <h5>Improved Accuracy</h5>
                        <p>With automated processing, e-invoicing eliminates manual data entry errors, ensuring more accurate invoices and fewer disputes between businesses.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Advantage 3 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="advantage-card p-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/icon-faster.png" alt="Faster Payments" width="50" class="mb-3">
                        <h5>Faster Payments</h5>
                        <p>E-Invoices are processed and delivered in real-time, significantly speeding up the invoicing lifecycle. This results in faster approval and quicker payment cycles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <!-- Advantage 4 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="advantage-card p-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/icon-security.png" alt="Enhanced Security" width="50" class="mb-3">
                        <h5>Enhanced Security</h5>
                        <p>E-Invoicing uses encrypted channels to ensure invoice data is securely exchanged, protecting sensitive financial information from fraud and cyber threats.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Advantage 5 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="advantage-card p-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/icon-environment.png" alt="Environmental Benefits" width="50" class="mb-3">
                        <h5>Environmental Benefits</h5>
                        <p>Cut down on paper usage and contribute to a greener environment by going digital. E-invoicing significantly reduces the need for printed documents, lowering your carbon footprint.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Advantage 6 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="advantage-card p-4 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/icon-compliance.png" alt="Regulatory Compliance" width="50" class="mb-3">
                        <h5>Regulatory Compliance</h5>
                        <p>Stay compliant with the latest tax regulations. E-invoicing helps you meet governmental requirements for invoice generation and storage, reducing audit risks.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="cta-section py-5 text-white bg-primary text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h3>Ready to Switch to E-Invoicing?</h3>
